Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Karino Daisuke?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.52,0:01:00.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,And Sister Yumiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, I regret to inform you
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.69,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that my St. Michaela Project has failed,\N because the academy girls rebelled.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.63,0:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To save Japan, I've joined a kamikaze unit \Nand am leaving for Okinawa tomorrow. {lit: special attack squad - what the Japanese called kamikaze}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.69,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of the Empire depends\N upon today's battle! {common pattern for the encouraging speech to the soldiers, modeled after Togo's "The fate of the Empire depends upon today's battle: let every man do his utmost" from the battle of tsushima}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.69,0:01:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have formed this special attack unit \Nto carry out a most heroic act of courage.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.35,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must promote the tradition\Nof the glorious Imperial Navy.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.45,0:01:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be an example of honor \Nfor the next generation to follow!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe out all of the enemy fleet,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,thereby building the foundation\Nof an immortal empire! {can't hear shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.61,0:01:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the end of Karino Daisuke? \NBut how on Earth...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.84,0:02:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.11,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoike Kumi of St. Michaela School.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.45,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at last, I shall...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.66,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall avenge Daisuke's death!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.21,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just horrible...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I am Aaron.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.98,0:04:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed Aoike Kumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But not Aiko! You're not planning to kill Aiko, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so loud!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.23,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have forgotten\Nyou're living on my terms.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could easily banish you here and now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare me that, Miss Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Strip down.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.34,0:05:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get it through to your body \Nthat you're my servant!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.35,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've surrendered your body to me, \Nbut your soul is still reserved for Aiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.51,0:06:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuki, if you kill Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.71,0:06:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I will commit suicide right here \Nand take you with me. { to sacrifice oneself in order to harm someone else}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I don't plan to do Aiko any harm whatsoever.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.97,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My objective is to send the Children's Crusade to Jerusalem, no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the Children's Crusade to Jerusalem?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.17,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you conniving against my comrades from St. Michaela?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your objectives are the same!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.34,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you love Aiko, \NI too have someone I love.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.94,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be on your way. \NWe're leaving tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.34,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my departure, \NI'd like us to have a wedding.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.54,0:08:38.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,If only Aiko Mimura hadn't\N come to St. Michaela,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,my dear Daisuke would not have died.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is kill Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Then he can't reincarnate as Mimura Aiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,Nor can he come into our time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Daisuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.36,0:08:57.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll do everything in my power\Nto protect your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuki intends to kill Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,I must do something, or Hans...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,No, rather, Aiko's life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.56,Top,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.56,0:09:18.48,Top,,0,0,0,,We pray that through your guidance we may safely reach the Holy Land of Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.48,0:09:20.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,That voice... Hans?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.52,0:09:25.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,I must tell him. \NIf we're destined to unite at some point,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.52,0:09:29.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,I will swallow my shame \Nand use my body to convince him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.11,Top,,0,0,0,,...so that the wind will be calm\N over the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.11,0:09:37.10,Top,,0,0,0,,Lord, keep your loving hand\Nof guidance upon our journey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.17,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You are Ikeda Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.74,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing here half-naked?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.88,0:09:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my fellows has died. \NA girl named Aoike Kumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.07,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening to us \Nwill happen to you as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.42,0:10:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We are now also a part \Nof your Children's Crusade.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is targeting you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you driving at?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.42,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you please cancel the expedition?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that again!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you. \NI was born for this mission.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.26,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year ago, someone stood\Nat my bedside and said:
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go to Jerusalem."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm sure I heard the Lord.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe in God?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is you, Hans, that I want to believe in.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.19,0:10:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've taught me a way of living\Nthat I could not have imagined.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.09,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When? I only just met you yesterday! {or maybe today, doesn't exactly say when}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have met before.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, we will meet\Nhundreds of years from now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lovers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? \NThat you've come backwards in time?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I don't blame you\N for not believing me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But back in my time, \Nyou were my first love.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First love?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We even consummated our love once, with our bodies. {actually just says colloquially "had sex"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.46,0:11:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is fate, if there is destiny, you need but to touch my skin to believe my heart. {literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's immoral!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With unspoiled purity as our shield,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.79,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we the Crusade must rise up \Nand proceed toward the Holy Land.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect your life with my own!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, you filth.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disaster!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.66,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans and the Children's Crusade \Nhave already departed!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, we've got to follow them.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, ready your gear \Nand meet up in 30 minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.45,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco, is everything okay\Nwith your carriage?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your order was so abrupt.\NWe had to leave in a hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a revelation from God.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are protected by the Lord, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Francois? You were supposed to be \Nin the carriage further back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.22,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I don't see those girls from Japan \Nwho came to support us anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'm sure they'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.24,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like we {\i1}need{\i0} their support.\NWe can manage fine on our own.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.77,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, I've heard rumors \Nof bandits that prey on pilgrims.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them try if they dare.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.42,0:13:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hand them their due\Npunishment, right, leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll spare no one that stands in our way.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandits!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them, you bums!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Francois!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.67,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.12,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the support from St. Michaela!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you underestimate us girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Girls' Crusade!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The veterans of a hundred battles...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.92,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...who wiped out the feudal army!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.88,0:15:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.89,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We just missed them. The Children's Crusade left early this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue's group too?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were led by Hans Heilner.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko, that's you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.96,0:15:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. I know the route\Nthey're taking to Marseilles.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To Marseilles!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To Marseilles!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here at last, Aiko.\NNo, Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Francois!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.89,0:16:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{inaudible prayers}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.50,0:17:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!\NTake her down!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her a burial!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.19,0:17:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against the Lord's word\N to take your own life,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how desperate you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.69,0:17:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans! Do you still believe in the Lord?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These trials are also God's will.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.29,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We will overcome all trials and surely reclaim the Holy City of Jerusalem!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Marco?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're burning up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Marco?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get his fever down.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo is making an herbal remedy \Nwith river water.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.46,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how you predicted\Nthe fever that's ailing Marco. {lit: it's incredible - just as you worried before you left, marco developed a fever -- I have no idea what he/she is talking about, there was no such episode previously in this or previous episode... perhaps they forgot to animate it? not like everything else in this show makes sense}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Aaron.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.71,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been sent directly\Nby the Pope to aid Hans. {/she}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.84,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you are God's messengers,\Ncapable of prophecy?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.77,0:18:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that. \NWe've come here denying God's existence.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.18,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's done.\NJust enough for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.38,0:18:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika, why don't you bring it to them?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. May I, Misayo?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll be joining you\N as soon as I make some more.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to make enough\Nto get us to Marseilles.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty handy, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.96,0:19:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like the medic of the St. Michaela troop.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can save someone else's life,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I bet you can't save yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.82,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo has been killed.\NThe killer is here among us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.84,0:20:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?! \NYou suspect us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.24,0:20:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo said, "The Children's Crusade,"\Nbefore drawing her last breath.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.95,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.78,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's stop this!\N This is no time to turn on one another.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika? Are you taking their side?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Watoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate any more insults from you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, every one of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.38,0:20:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco, you should be in bed!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.41,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault. \NIf only I hadn't caught this fever...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo would still be alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault... {unsure what this minna means}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.71,0:20:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Misayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's give Misayo a proper burial.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.96,0:21:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've failed to keep them from advancing, \Nand they made it to Marseilles.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumi's dead. So is Misayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.10,0:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't left Aiko behind and gone\N without her, maybe they wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Watoko, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Kozue.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have waited\N for Aiko to recover!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.29,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here, and nothing can be done about it now, can it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.80,0:21:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.26,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.20,0:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not far from Marseilles.\NHang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.09,0:22:11.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,I must avert Yuki's evil plot. \NOr else, I will vanish from this world. {probably refers to some time paradox, though it's a bit late to think about it now lol; officials had it "evaporate"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.98,0:22:16.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,And the Amakusa Restoration, the world\N without nations or religions, will never happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can smell the sea breeze.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.40,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea! Hey, it's the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the Mediterranean!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.53,0:23:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it! \NJerusalem is just beyond this sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.85,0:23:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God, our Lord, has indeed seen us\N through our journey.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord. \NAnd thank you, Kozue and fellows.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you're on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.54,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you still hold a grudge against us?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.00,0:23:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.43,0:23:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid the Mediterranean won't part for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.75,0:23:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.95,0:23:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no miracle.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when you'll finally realize the Pope has betrayed you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.72,0:23:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.91,0:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, you've been betrayed by\Nthe very religion you cherished.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.60,0:23:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie! {/no way}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.68,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be sold to a slave ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.18,0:23:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Waving a contract with the Pope, the traders will take you all to Africa!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.15,0:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mocking us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.51,0:23:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.38,0:23:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We must pray.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.68,0:23:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A miracle will happen.\NThe sea will part.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.09,0:23:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We will get to the Holy Land.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.77,0:23:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we believe in Him, the Lord will hear us and answer our prayers!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.63,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Hans is right!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.54,0:24:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us pray.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.01,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Father who art in heaven...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.70,0:24:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Father who art in heaven.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.20,0:24:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We the Crusaders have come here to take back Holy Jerusalem from the heathens.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, please open our way\Nthrough the Mediterranean.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.94,0:24:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.09,0:24:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.54,0:25:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The sea is swelling!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:40.16,0:25:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.00,0:25:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is parting!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.68,0:26:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to the Holy Land\Nhas been opened.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:13.80,0:26:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's proceed to Jerusalem!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.97,0:26:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To Jerusalem!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.85,0:26:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.85,0:26:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue, you have nothing more to tell us.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:27.10,0:26:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea has parted.\NThe promise has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.36,0:26:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those slave traders you feared\Nare nowhere in sight.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:32.99,0:26:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening.\NIt's impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.89,0:26:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be some sort of trickery!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:39.70,0:26:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be deceived!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.08,0:26:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:43.55,0:26:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These women have only pretended\Nto support our cause!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:47.88,0:26:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaron!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.93,0:26:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what they said?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:51.72,0:26:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If the sea doesn't part, it proves to us\N that the Pope has lied about everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.56,0:26:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the sea did part!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:59.44,0:27:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After witnessing a miracle,\Nwhy would they still deny it?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:03.07,0:27:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they are fallen angels\Ntrying to destroy the Pope!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.24,0:27:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the Devil's servants!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.49,0:27:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.12,0:27:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them to me to handle.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:12.97,0:27:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans, lead your fellows across the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.29,0:27:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:23.41,0:27:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cross the sea together.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:26.27,0:27:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Rika has true faith in the Lord.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:30.72,0:27:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!\NWe're crossing the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.51,0:27:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:42.29,0:27:48.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,Kozue, forgive me. \NI'm doing this for Hans... no, Aiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.13,0:27:49.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:59.81,0:28:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Watoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.29,0:28:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.41,0:28:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.00,0:28:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kumi and Misayo?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:11.59,0:28:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All wiped out, most likely.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:15.10,0:28:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:22.18,0:28:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-san, I presume?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.65,0:28:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I've been waiting for you, \NMimura Aiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:29.02,0:28:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You would disrupt the peaceful flow of time just for one man?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:33.88,0:28:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't expect you to understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.48,0:28:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to resurrect the dreadful Michaela Project once again?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:40.89,0:28:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Michaela Project doesn't have to happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.39,0:28:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to resurrect the dark history \Non behalf of Karino Daisuke, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:51.95,0:28:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:52.91,0:28:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke belongs to me alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:55.13,0:28:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep him from going to St. Michaela.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:57.77,0:29:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:01.20,0:29:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:02.62,0:29:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In this timeline, the uprising at St. Michaela\N will serve as a springboard
Dialogue: 10,0:29:07.60,0:29:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Amakusa Restoration, and ultimately the World Restoration as well, regardless. {where they are now}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:11.67,0:29:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Karino Daisuke will disappear again in the tide of a new history.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.07,0:29:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary!\NIt's you who will disappear!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.19,0:29:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:03.62,0:30:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:04.34,0:30:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no longer {\i1}our{\i0} Kozue and the girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:07.06,0:30:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only zombies, \Nmanipulated by Yuki's sorcery!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.21,0:30:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.80,0:30:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill or be killed.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.67,0:30:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use fighting back.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:33.73,0:30:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwadate!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.73,0:30:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.21,0:30:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Mimura Aiko, you're the only one left!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.41,0:30:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good friend and follow\Nthe others to Hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:46.87,0:30:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:59.59,0:31:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Try manipulating them now!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:01.76,0:31:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:05.52,0:31:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaron!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.19,0:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaron!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.48,0:31:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaron!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:17.50,0:31:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.53,0:31:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We were worried, so we came back.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.54,0:31:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierre, Johann, Marco, Michel...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.45,0:31:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.15,0:31:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! It's me, Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:31.66,0:31:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierre, Johann, Marco, Michel...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:37.35,0:31:38.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,Rika?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.92,0:31:41.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:41.88,0:31:44.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,What... You were alive?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:44.49,0:31:48.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,There she is. I'm finally seeing Aiko again!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:48.56,0:31:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.63,0:31:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:51.51,0:31:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:52.81,0:31:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the leader of the Devil's support troop, the girls of St. Michaela, Mimura Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:58.44,0:32:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the Devil!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.32,0:32:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it! \NI don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:09.62,0:32:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stop resisting! {resistance is futile}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:13.31,0:32:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Michel!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:14.53,0:32:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice! \NI'll just have to make you sleep awhile.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:25.22,0:32:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:26.22,0:32:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann! Marco! Pierre! Michel!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:28.93,0:32:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:30.81,0:32:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann! Marco! Pierre! Michel!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:35.35,0:32:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans, let me explain.\NThere's a reason for this...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:38.57,0:32:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:41.35,0:32:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:42.99,0:32:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hans Heilner.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:44.81,0:32:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:46.70,0:32:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are me.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.78,0:32:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:49.95,0:32:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.34,0:32:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't hurt me.\NIt'll be a catastrophe for everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:55.87,0:32:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Hans. She {\i1}is{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.08,0:33:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:22.43,0:33:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.21,0:33:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:28.12,0:33:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:37.00,0:33:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it at last!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.33,0:33:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've destroyed Mimura Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.05,0:33:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, I'll fly over to you right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:59.62,0:34:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke... Daisuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:04.28,0:34:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:07.40,0:34:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:10.54,0:34:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... we finally meet again!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:13.79,0:34:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, 735 years from now, \NI will be able to live out my life with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.75,0:34:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:21.41,0:34:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have sunk to the bottom \Nof the southern sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.82,0:34:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to die this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.67,0:34:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go back to the time\Nbefore our wedding.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.34,0:34:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible, Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:32.11,0:34:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There, look at that.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:40.77,0:34:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But that's...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.88,0:34:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it has begun. \NThe World Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:46.11,0:34:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The World Restoration?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:48.32,0:34:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Daisuke!\NWho are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.65,0:34:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:56.78,0:34:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.66,0:35:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:01.62,0:35:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Karino Daisuke has disappeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.79,0:35:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the World Restoration\Nhas become a reality,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:07.89,0:35:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,his existence has no place\Nin this particular space and time.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:11.46,0:35:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stop this vile World Restoration!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:14.60,0:35:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:42.37,0:35:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Holiness! You're unharmed.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:44.37,0:35:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Aaron!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:46.09,0:35:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This is your doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:49.29,0:35:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:51.25,0:35:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Children's Crusade that left for Jerusalem
Dialogue: 10,0:35:54.36,0:35:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,has returned to attack us because of a contract\N they found on some slave dealers' ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.61,0:36:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This must be some sort of conspiracy \Nthat you instigated!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:04.23,0:36:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I tell you, he's a hermaphrodite!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:07.74,0:36:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Devil's messenger!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:10.69,0:36:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:16.66,0:36:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:20.16,0:36:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A hermaphrodite! How did this happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:22.70,0:36:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't keep it alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:24.21,0:36:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We must kill it!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:27.31,0:36:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You wretched creatures...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:29.51,0:36:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all burn in the fires of Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:45.52,0:36:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Forgive me...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:48.52,0:36:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't kill me.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:52.07,0:36:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare my measly life! I beg you!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.25,0:37:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:15.51,0:37:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Devil...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:18.07,0:37:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool. It is you who will end up in Hell.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:39.53,0:37:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Restoration has been completed.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:41.93,0:37:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:43.37,0:37:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Sage!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:44.74,0:37:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were alive?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.33,0:37:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just sealed it yourself, dear Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.24,0:37:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've now completed\N the World Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:55.59,0:37:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Old Sage?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:58.28,0:38:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All these events were preordained, Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:02.68,0:38:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From the founding of St. Michaela School, to the student uprising,
Dialogue: 10,0:38:07.13,0:38:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the Amakusa Restoration, \Nall the way to the World Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:11.62,0:38:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All were merely playing a part\Nin the history of this world. {maybe "space and time"}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:20.12,0:38:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Yuki. Try to remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.22,0:38:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How peaceful and plentiful was\N the world post-Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:39.17,0:38:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But for Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:42.58,0:38:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:43.91,0:38:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are tied to the dark history \Nare doomed to perish.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:48.77,0:38:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Old Sage, your explanation doesn't convince me!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:53.63,0:38:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yayoi! You're alive?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:55.81,0:38:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimura Aiko! Ikeda Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:59.30,0:39:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:00.50,0:39:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way! This is ludicrous!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.24,0:39:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuki, even you can't touch Hans-Aiko now.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:09.88,0:39:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have become one with Hans, completely.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:13.66,0:39:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Rika and Yayoi over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:17.71,0:39:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We too have been rescued by Yayoi.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:21.57,0:39:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I don't remember ever\Nbeing killed, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:26.77,0:39:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had to tweak time a little, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.76,0:39:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Sage, who on Earth are you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:35.82,0:39:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, you even forgot that?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:40.74,0:39:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:41.86,0:39:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:44.72,0:39:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yuki. Try to remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:46.88,0:39:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember those who have lived deep\N within the dark and oppressed history.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:53.15,0:39:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonza!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:54.68,0:39:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But your appearance...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:57.05,0:39:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Gonza has reincarnated\N for the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:59.94,0:40:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He is precisely the one true symbol \Nof the World Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:06.22,0:40:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I suppose it's now time for me\Nto make claims on your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:11.91,0:40:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Sage!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:14.44,0:40:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Time, be still. You are beautiful."
Dialogue: 10,0:40:18.98,0:40:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say you don't remember\Nthe pact we made that day.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:23.85,0:40:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have yet to meet Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:30.05,0:40:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, just like Indra's net,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:33.22,0:40:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,all the worlds are held together by\N the reflections they cast on each other.{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indra's_net}{lit: by casting shadows, form the whole}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:39.81,0:40:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we have fulfilled our mission, \Nthere's no need for us to stay in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:45.47,0:40:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can understand that too.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:47.70,0:40:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only wanted... to be with Daisuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:53.68,0:40:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Sage, brace yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:56.89,0:40:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:00.65,0:41:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Mimura Aiko!\NYou {\i1}still{\i0} won't get out of my way?!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:11.45,0:41:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:14.62,0:41:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I protected the one I love...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:18.23,0:41:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko, I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:21.74,0:41:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:30.20,0:41:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of you, Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:36.41,0:41:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke... I'm coming to you now...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:46.28,0:41:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, be still. You are beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:16.27,0:42:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:18.02,0:42:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:20.31,0:42:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke! Here we are at last!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:23.71,0:42:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be together forever now.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:27.30,0:42:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:28.70,0:42:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:31.27,0:42:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:34.58,0:42:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika, hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:36.70,0:42:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Yayoi for some medicine for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:41.88,0:42:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.96,0:42:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Yuki is gone, \Nmy second life is about to expire too.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:51.09,0:42:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:55.64,0:43:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no greater joy\Nthan to die in your arms.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:01.74,0:43:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika, my heart... will always\Nbelong to you alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:09.74,0:43:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:21.83,0:43:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:25.13,0:43:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:01.76,0:44:05.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,I won't forget you, I promise, Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:05.14,0:44:11.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,As long as this world goes on, \Nyou'll keep on living in my heart forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:13.68,0:44:15.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:16.61,0:44:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:18.90,0:44:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:05.80,Song,,0,0,0,,{the song is likely "光(yasashisa)につつまれて" by 上田浩恵; couldn't find so much as a mention of it on the internet, let alone any trace of lyrics; translating by ear}The wind blows through the gaps in the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:12.08,Song,,0,0,0,,And the radiance of freedom pours through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:16.85,Song,,0,0,0,,I gathered it with both my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:22.20,Song,,0,0,0,,And kept searching until I found my true feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:28.83,Song,,0,0,0,,While seeing gentle dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:42.56,Song,,0,0,0,,Even the days when I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:49.27,Song,,0,0,0,,While staring at the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:04:00.40,Song,,0,0,0,,Those days no longer exist
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.00,0:45:09.78,Song,,0,0,0,,{Tears are Bells ~櫂 by Torsten Rasch and Ueda Hiroe again; unlike the OP, this one is strangely well preserved and available for official streaming, but still no trace of lyrics; translating by ear }I've been waiting for your hand forever
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.78,0:45:31.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Drowning and sinking in the depths of sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.87,0:45:43.49,Song,,0,0,0,,Freed from all doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.49,0:45:56.48,Song,,0,0,0,,I dream of the time when I could swim freely
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.48,0:46:01.19,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm born again
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.15,0:46:14.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Over the waves, beyond the sea,\N the wind will blow me to the faraway land
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.45,0:46:27.80,Song,,0,0,0,,Let the ship sail away in search of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.05,0:46:40.09,Song,,0,0,0,,{the credits said the english lyrics are by rasch the composer himself}You are best and best I need
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.09,0:46:45.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Taking all the sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.97,0:46:54.70,Song,,0,0,0,,This is the bleeding heart
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.70,0:47:08.97,Song,,0,0,0,,Now the echo starts to rewind here
